              , lastContextMenuOrSubmenu
                    >> Maybe.andThen (menuEntryContainingTextIgnoringCase "asteroid belts")
                    >> Maybe.map (.uiNode >> clickOnUIElement MouseButtonLeft >> List.singleton)
              )
            , ( "Click on one of the menu entries."
